{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"body":"Cross-ticket note: the audit-trail UI epic 2141-0ba0-5313-48d4 (browser dashboard, FastAPI/[reviewbot] extra) is ORTHOGONAL to this transport — different stack/protocol/audience/files/config. Only shared concern: both default to loopback :8000, so keep http_port configurable (already the design) to avoid a runtime clash if both run on one host. No dependency edge or shared HTTP util is warranted (would be premature coupling)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784090715265155001,"uuid":"1e9f63ad-67e6-4d0d-a9d6-0b047ad8c459"}